text: Located in the desirable Cedar Heights community is this impeccably maintained 3 bed/2.5 bath home! Welcomed by a covered front porch, the main floor features fresh paint throughout. The entry and den leads to open concept dining, family room & kitchen with stainless steel appliances, newer granite countertops, sink and updated flooring throughout. Through the slider is the beautifully landscaped and private fully-fenced backyard including covered deck for entertaining! Laundry room located across from the guest bath and 2-car garage access nearby. Upstairs you are greeted with the spacious primary bedroom with jetted tub and large walk-in closet. Second full bath and 2 more bedrooms with beautiful mountainous views! Welcome Home!

Welcome to Spring Meadows! This charming residence features a great 4-bedroom, 1.75-bath floorplan with vaulted ceilings, a generous kitchen, and a cozy fireplace. Enjoy ample natural light throughout, complemented by a landscaped fenced yard. While the rear deck leads to a private artist shed. the home is located near a community park and playground with a peaceful greenbelt & convenient gate access. Residents can explore nearby walking trails, biking paths, and a serene pond. Exciting, NEW Ring security cameras overlooking the park, garage, and at the doorbell. A free-floating island rounds out the space in the kitchen to provide a versatile area. See this home now!

Showcase lot! Prime waterfront living on this nearly acre property, boasting over 200 feet of coveted low bank waterfront. Every room positioned to capture breathtaking views from the majestic Rainbow Bridge to the tranquil south end of the Swinomish Channel. Entertain with ease in the inviting great room, ideal for hosting gatherings or unwinding with loved ones. 3 bedroom rambler w/ oversized primary + 2 additional bedrooms flexible for crafting or office space. Wrap around deck & private patio creates an unforgettable backdrop for al fresco dining & sunset cocktails. The lower level casita retreat offers privacy & flex-space with a bedroom, twin day beds, bathroom & kitchenette. Nestled on a mature, private lot, this gem is a rare find.

Make this well kept 3 bedroom 2 full bath home yours.This home features vaulted ceiling w/ceiling fans. Master bedroom with private bathroom.Walk out your back door onto your back deck looking out into own private oasis in your back yard.backyard is fully fenced . Here is your opportunity to enjoy safety and security in one of the nicest 55+parks.this home has to small sheds for storage

Welcome to your new home! This delightful 773 square-foot home is perfect for those seeking a cozy and charming living space. Nestled in the heart of Sedro-Woolley this 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers both comfort and convenience. Step into the kitchen that perfectly combines charm and functionality. With tons of natural light and a quaint breakfast nook its perfect for your morning coffee. Step outside to your fully fenced yard, plenty of room for play and relaxation. The property also features a small one car garage and secure alley access parking, offering a discreet and reliable place for parking your vehicles. This home has it all! Come check it out today!

RARE OPPORTUNITY for Investors or primary residence! This well cared for Duplex is located on beautiful lot w/a MASSIVE 1800sqft shop and 2 car garage w/office. Unit 1 is owner occupied with 2 beds, .75bath, bonus room, spacious living room, kitchen and utility room/mud room. Pellet stove to keep you warm in winter and ceiling fans and window A/C unit to cool you down in summer. Unit 2 with long-term tenant has 1 bed with patio access, kitchen with eating area 1 bath. Spacious backyard w/beautiful garden beds, fruit trees, partially fenced w/shop access through gate. Shop has plenty of storage, work benches and room for all your toys and projects. 2 car garage w/generous storage throughout leads to office or craft space. Great location!

Rare lot in the city of Sedro Woolley, with all utilities on site. Condemned home on property may be salvageable. Great location and level lot, ready for your vision. Seller/builder has conceptual drawings for a mixed commercial/apartment style building and will work with buyer should they want to pursue this avenue. City of SW prefers this type of structure but has indicated they will allow the current home to be rehabbed. Buyer to verify potential uses and zoning with the city of Sedro Woolley.

This is the one you've been waiting for! Burlington's Best home is situated on a quiet corner lot within walking distance of shopping, schools, transit, the neighborhood park, and more. Charming elegance of the past meets modern style of today - with floors and roof having been updated recently, as well as new paint, new cabinets/countertops, new light fixtures, and a new sewer line! The large kitchen affords a small eating space, with room for a dining table in the family room. Natural light pours into the bedrooms and throughout the house! Every square foot has been thoughtfully cared for with a purpose in this cozy space. Mature foliage out front and in the yard provides plenty of opportunity for garden dreams to come true. Welcome Home!

Discover a prime opportunity to own nearly 40 acres in South Skagit. This expansive property carries dual zoning designations, offering both agricultural and recreational possibilities. Enjoy the rural setting with picturesque views of the Cascade Mountains, with quick easy access to all the amenities of town. This parcel is perfect for farmers, investors, or those looking to build a custom farmstead amidst natural beauty. No studies have been performed on the property and is being sold As-Is as part of an estate sale.

This mobile has been extensively remodeled. The Roof was replaced by Cascade Roofing in 2021 All Appliances were replaced in 2021 New furnace and deck in 2021 Fresh paint inside and out Flooring was all updated as well. A new pass bar with extra cabinetry was added to the kitchen space. This home also boasts large extra tip-out space great for a home office or extra large living room space. This lovely home is located in 55+ park in the last space, covered carport has a 10x10 storage unit and covered parking for 2. Nice private space in the back for patio furniture space to add gardening boxes. Quiet Park is near I-5 minutes from downtown MV and waterfront walking trails, Fairgrounds, and the community center.

Great chance to own 5.86 acres near Lake McMurray with septic installed. Great property for recreation or investment. Property will require a rain catchment system for water if buyer intends to build. Lot cert on file, septic as built and permit recorded online. Septic installed, but in unknown condition. Buyer to verify all to buyer's satisfaction.

Discover this extraordinary custom-built luxury home, featuring 3461 sqft on a half-acre landscaped lot offering privacy and Northwest living. The main floor boasts a spacious open great room with vaulted ceilings, skylights, and expansive views. The chef's kitchen includes custom cabinets, pull-outs, under-counter lighting, a custom tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry. The primary suite offers a grand custom tile shower, spacious walk-in closet, and champagne bronze fixtures. Downstairs features a media room, office, full bath, and flex room/ 4th bedroom. Outside, enjoy a fenced yard with a covered heated patio, gas BBQ, fire pit, and fenced yard. Includes a massive four-car garage. Ideal for luxury seekers in a serene setting.

Wow! One of these condos rarely hit the market! This condo has just been redone with new interior paint, new vinyl plank flooring, new heaters, new bath, new 2 faux wood blinds throughout. Interbay is a condo association with 12 units, each with a single car garage and storage room. This unit is 2 bedrooms, 1 bath located on the main level. The kitchen offers refrigerator, dishwasher, stove and the laundry includes the washer and dryer. There is a nice covered patio plus a 23' dock!! Priced to sell!

Welcome to your next home in a fantastic location! This property features 4 bedrooms & a large, almost fully fenced yard, perfect for many buyers. The upper level boasts a spacious living room, kitchen, dining area, balcony for entertaining, 2 bedrooms, & 1 bathroom. The lower level offers two additional bedrooms, a half bath, utility area & storage closet. Oversized single-car garage provides ample storage space & backyard access, while large deck above ideal for BBQs & relaxing. Recent updates include relatively new metal garage door & fresh paint on house 4-5 years ago. There's also a convenient storage shed located on the south side of the property. Close location to all essential services, this home offers both comfort & convenience.

Beautiful 2BR, 1.75BA condo in lovely 55 & Better community offers the very best in serene living! So many features to love - new vinyl plank floors, heat pump for cooling, single-level layout w/vaulted ceilings in the living rm and cozy gas fireplace. Your primary suite with attached bath features a spacious walk-in closet + an extra private feel with views of the trees & greenbelt behind. The front porch & partially covered back deck are the best seats in the house for enjoying the surrounding nature, the neighboring creek and water feature views. 2-car garage offers plenty of storage space for hobbies. Great location near medical and shopping yet private and quiet - there's even a community trail with private gate leading to Haggen.

Craftsman Home, 40x60 Shop on 10 acres...Picture a cozy living room with a river rock fireplace, sunlight streaming through high windows, and hickory floors leading to a kitchen adorned with alder cabinets. This home is a harmonious blend of natural materials and thoughtful design. The home is 2736 sq ft, 3 bdrms, 2 bths, on upper floor, den/office, 3/4 bthrm, spacious dining rm, kitchen with granite counters, eating bar & walk-in pantry on main floor. Unfinished bonus room over garage has future access from upstairs hall. Shop has additional studio space, full bthrm, loft storage area & 3 bays w/14' doors. Private setting, garden space, partially fenced & convenient to I-5.

Bring your imagination. This property provides the most tranquil setting. Enjoy all nature has to offer on your private 6.2 acres. This 1995 manufactured home has plenty of space, with well-sized bedrooms and two full baths. The kitchen provides a large eating area. The front deck provides plenty of room for entertainment. There is a 20X30 metal shop with a metal roof that includes a 10X10 backroom with a bath. The property also boasts a woodshed, gazebo, play equipment and a chicken coop. There are great recreational areas nearby, and only a short drive to the town of Sedro-Wooley and all the conveniences. Welcome Home!

Discover the perfect spot for your camper, RV, or a manufactured home in the Cape Horn community. This versatile lot is ideal for year-round living or as a weekend getaway. With water and electricity conveniently available at the street, setting up is a breeze. Enjoy easy access to the stunning Skagit River, perfect for fishing enthusiasts and nature lovers. The community park enhances your experience with amenities like a playground, a gazebo with picnic tables, a basketball court, making it perfect for gatherings and leisurely activities. Explore the numerous nearby trails and immerse yourself in the natural beauty of the Pacific NW. Build your dream home & savor all that this enchanting location has to offer. Your adventure begins here!

Three quarter acre property on Fir Island with older home, detached garage and shop! House has been converted into two units, shop has been converted into living space. Convenient to I-5 and surrounded by open farmland with some of the best soils in the state! House needs updating, bring you toolkit and polish it up! Great potential!
